Turns out the late Paul Walker had a handsome car collection , and those cars are going on sale , TMZ reports .

The actor was as much a car guy in real life as on screen , and has amassed a collection of approximately 30 cars , some of which have previously been featured in the media , and some of which have not .

The only other known Paul Walker car which has recently been offered for sale is a Nissan Skyline R34 GT - R owned by a Munich - based tuning shop called GT - A , which acquired the car after federal agents in Costa Mesa , Calif .

The German shop offered the car for 1 million euros , promising to donate half the proceeds to Walker 's charity , Reach Out Worldwide , though in the three months that it has been on sale no word of a deal has emerged .
